I’m not sure about OpenStudio specifically, but it looks like you’re running an annual simulation. The last line seems to represent timestep 1 (January) 8 at 11:00:00 AM. Wouldn’t you expect it to keep going until it gets to 12 31 23:00:00 for December 31?
